#- Chapter 1§0
§0    Founders§0
§0
§0Section 1 - Dollaz & Gobblin are the founders of Ruin. Any major changes to the city are firstly to be confirmed by one of the two.§0

#- Chapter 2§0
§0    Council Members§0
§0
§0Section 1 - Council members are in charge of a responsibility each, the current council members are anon_one1 (Security, External Affairs) & the_JKH (Public Relations).
#- Chapter 3§0
§0    Citizens§0
§0        (Trusted)§0
§0
§0Section 1 - These citizens have access to public city storage, with the expectation that while they are free to take as they please, and they are also able to contribute back into the city.
#- Section 2 - Trusted citizens are citizens that either;§0
§0(a) Have come from a previous settlement that has involved one of the council members or founders who can vouch for proven trustworthiness. 
#- (b) Have lived in the city and integrated into the community successfully, gaining the trust of council members and founders. 
#- Chapter 4§0
§0    Citizens (New)§0
§0
§0Section 1 - These citizens have recently joined the town and have no prior connection to any founder or council members. These citizens do not have access to public city storage,
#- but can access select city factories & buildings.§0
§0Section 2 - For a new player to become trusted they must prove§0
§0(a) Dedication: Through the construction of their home by gathering their 
#- own resources and putting their time into construction.§0
§0(b) Knowledge: By making use of city infrastructure such as the factories, they can prove their understanding of vital server plugins.
#- (c) Contribution: By contributing back into the city through assisting with whole town projects. 
#- Chapter 5§0
§0    Guests§0
§0
§0Section 1 - These players are welcome into the town, may participate in town chat and discord channels. They may have access to the city factories at the discretion of founders & council members.
#- Chapter 6§0
§0    Persona§0
§0        Non Grata§0
§0
§0Section 1 - These players are not welcome into the town and may have been deemed unwelcome under various circumstances.  Such a person 
#- may only enter the town, escorted by a Citizen under permission of a Council Member.
#- 